{"tid":1915371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★買樓抗炎大法！中原：2月十大屋苑交投創3個月新高 顯示買家積極入市","createTime":"2020-03-08T07:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T04:42:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e980b4eca7b63ac10acfbd376fa5ba020b2bd9da","tid":1915371,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"中原地產研究部高級聯席董事黃良昇指出，2020年2月份十大藍籌屋苑的二手買賣合約登記錄得221宗，總值18.92億元，按月分別上升54.5%及61.5%。數字是自2019年11月的288宗及22.81億元之後，創三個月新高。2月份登記反映1月期間的市況，顯示新春前有買家提早積極入市，二手樓市氣氛活躍，帶動大型屋苑交投上揚<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200308/bkn-20200308134551717-0308_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200308%2Fbkn-20200308134551717-0308_00842_001.html&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=74969557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200308/bkn-20200308134551717-0308_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"59dc63fbb569971ad4afcc3667f99b2d6176cc94","tid":1915371,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:19:15.000Z","msg":"買樓抗炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1c030dae2482c78ef901cce31846da97f62fcf","tid":1915371,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位朋友, 幫手發這個聯署出去, 幫手找人簽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZ